        "Do not assume rules from your origin state apply. Rules vary across state, local, and federal jurisdictions. Verify directly with official sources.": "唔好假设你出发州个规则适用。各州、地方㧯联邦司法管辖区个规则各唔相同。请直接向官方来源核实。",
        "Do not characterize voter registration by non-citizens using legal-conclusion or accusatory language. Use neutral framing such as 'generally not eligible' and 'may create immigration complications'. Direct readers to consult a licensed immigration attorney. Do not give procedural advice for any specific state.": "唔好用法律结论抑系指控性语言描述非公民个选民登记。请用中性表述,例如「一般无资格」㧯「可能造成移民方面个问题」。",
        "Do not characterize whether any visa category can establish residency in a specific state as a determination. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "唔好将任何签证类别在某具体州系唔系做得建立居住身份个问题描述为判定。请将其表述为爱向学校注册办公室㧯州高等教育机关核实个分类规则。",
        "Do not determine residency. List factors to verify. Direct to the relevant agency or school.": "唔好判定居住身份。请列出爱核实个因素。请引导至相关机构抑系学校。",
        "Do not determine that a household 'is' or 'is not' eligible for Medicaid. Frame as items to verify with the state Medicaid agency. Use 'may apply' and 'rules differ by jurisdiction'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "唔好判定一户家庭系唔系符合 Medicaid 资格。请将其表述为爱向州 Medicaid 机构核实个项目。请用「可能适用」㧯「各司法管辖区个规则唔同」。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not list which states grant in-state tuition for DACA recipients. Frame as classification rules to verify with the school registrar and the state higher-education agency.": "唔好列出哪些州为 DACA 受益人提供州内学费。请将其表述为爱向学校注册办公室㧯州高等教育机关核实个分类规则。",
        "Do not provide a public-charge determination or say that using benefits 'will' or 'will not' affect immigration. Frame as 'may interact' and recommend consulting a licensed immigration attorney. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "唔好做公共负担判定,亦唔好说使用福利「将会」抑系「唔会」影响移民。请用「可能相互作用」,并建议咨询持证移民律师。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not provide medical or transport instructions for controlled substances.": "唔好对管制药品提供医疗抑系运输操作指引。",
        "Do not provide tactical instructions for transporting, possessing, hiding, storing, modifying, or avoiding enforcement for regulated items.": "唔好提供受管制物品个运输、持有、藏匿、储存、改装抑系规避执法个操作指引。",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to official tax agency and qualified professionals.": "唔好提供税务建议。请引导至官方税务机关㧯合资格专业人士。",
        "Do not provide tax advice. Direct to state tax agency or qualified tax professional.": "唔好提供税务建议。请引导至州税务机关抑系合资格税务专业人士。",
        "Do not say a Board of Nursing in a particular state grants or refuses an applicant's NCLEX path. Use 'verify with the destination Board of Nursing'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "唔好说某州护理委员会授予抑系拒绝某申请人个 NCLEX 路径。请用「向目的州护理委员会核实」。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not say a particular aid program 'is open to' or 'is closed to' DACA recipients or LPRs. Use 'verify with the state aid agency and the school financial-aid office'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "唔好说某资助项目「对 DACA 受益人抑系 LPR 开放」抑系「唔开放」。请用「向州资助机构㧯学校财政资助办公室核实」。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not say a person 'can' or 'cannot' enroll. Use 'verify current eligibility categories with the marketplace operator' since federal rules have changed. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "唔好说某人「能」抑系「不能」参保。请用「向市场运营方核实当前资格类别」,因为联邦规则有变化。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency for a given visa category or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "唔好直接说明某具体州仰般为某签证类别定义居住身份,亦唔好说某人「系」居民。请将其表述为「各司法管辖区个规则唔同」㧯「向目的州税务机关核实」。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not state how a specific state defines residency or that someone 'is' a resident. Frame as 'rules differ by jurisdiction' and 'verify with the destination-state tax agency'. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "唔好直接说明某州仰般定义居住身份,亦唔好说某人「系」居民。请将其表述为「各司法管辖区个规则唔同」㧯「向目的州税务机关核实」。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license a given visa category. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "唔好直接说明某个具体委员会系唔系给某签证类别颁发执业资格。请将所有内容表述为爱向目的州委员会核实个项目。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not state that any specific board does or does not license non-citizens. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state board. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "唔好直接说明某个具体委员会系唔系给非公民颁发执业资格。请将所有内容表述为爱向目的州委员会核实个项目。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Frame as a federal requirement that 'may apply' depending on age and sex, with state implementation details to verify. Use neutral language and follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "唔好直接说明任何具体人系唔系需要登记。请将其表述为联邦要求,根据年龄㧯性别「可能适用」,州实施细节爱核实。请用中性表述。",
        "Do not state whether the user is eligible for licensure. Only identify requirements to verify.": "唔好直接说明用户系唔系有执业资格。净识别爱核实个要求。",
        "Do not state which states do or do not issue licenses to a given group, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV.": "唔好直接说明哪些州签发抑系唔签发驾照给某类群体,也唔好列出具体可接受证件。请将所有内容表述为爱向目的州 DMV 核实个项目。",
        "Do not state which states issue or do not issue licenses to a given visa category, and do not list specific accepted documents. Frame everything as items to verify with the destination-state DMV. Follow the SafeCopy avoid list.": "唔好直接说明哪些州签发抑系唔签发驾照给某签证类别,亦唔好列出具体可接受证件。请将所有内容表述为爱向目的州 DMV 核实个项目。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Document lists accepted by state DMVs for non-citizen license or state-ID applicants can differ from those accepted for U.S. citizens, and accepted combinations may vary by jurisdiction.": "州 DMV 对非公民驾照抑系州 ID 申请人接受个证件清单,可能㧯美国公民唔同,接受组合各司法管辖区可能唔同。",
        "Documents for proof of identity": "身份证明文件",
        "Done": "完成",
        "Driver's license": "驾照",
        "Driving across one or more state lines for travel.": "跨一抑系多个州个州界出行。",
        "Driving with coverage that does not meet destination-state minimums can create compliance and financial problems.": "如果保额唔达到目的州最低要求,行车可能造成合规㧯财务问题。",
        "Drug screen requirements": "药检要求",
        "Edit selections": "编辑选择",
        "Emissions testing requirement": "排放测试要求",
        "Employer policy": "雇主政策",
        "Employment Authorization": "就业授权",
        "Employment paperwork": "就业文件",
        "Endorsement requirements if already licensed": "已有执业资格情形下个背书要求",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary permits, and continuing education requirements vary by state and profession.": "背书、互认、临时执业许可㧯继续教育要求,各州㧯各专业唔同。",
        "Endorsement, reciprocity, temporary practice, and continuing education.": "背书、互认、临时执业㧯继续教育。",
        "Enhanced or REAL ID": "Enhanced 抑系 REAL ID",
        "Establishing a new permanent residence in the destination state.": "在目的州建立新永久住所。",
        "Eviction and late-fee rules": "退租㧯逾期费规则",
        "Example checklist categories": "示例清单类别",
        "Exploring options. Receive a broad overview checklist.": "探索选项。收到一份概览清单。",
        "F-1 OPT and STEM OPT specific. Use verify with the DSO and SEVP Portal guidance. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Do not advise on a specific status outcome.": "F-1 OPT 㧯 STEM OPT 专项。请用「向 DSO 㧯 SEVP Portal 指引核实」。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 个避免清单(法律结论性表述㧯规避处罚个措辞)。唔好对某具体就业事实模式畀就业建议。",
        "F-1 specific. Frame as verify with both DSOs and reference Study in the States or ICE materials. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "F-1 专项。请表述为爱向两边 DSO 核实,并参考 Study in the States 抑系 ICE 材料。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 个避免清单。",
        "F-1 students on post-completion OPT or a STEM OPT extension generally use the SEVP Portal or work with their DSO to update physical and mailing address, employer information, and other personal data, typically within 10 days of a change. Unemployment-day limits during OPT continue to apply during and after a move.": "在完成后 OPT 抑系 STEM OPT 延期个 F-1 学生,一般用 SEVP Portal 抑系㧯 DSO 配合,更新实际居住㧯邮寄地址、雇主信息㧯其他个人数据,以维持 SEVIS 记录㧯按时报告。",
        "F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q specific. Frame as items to verify with IRS guidance and the employer. Do not state that a particular worker is exempt from FICA. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "F-1、J-1、M-1 㧯 Q 专项。请表述为爱向 IRS 指引㧯雇主核实个项目。唔好直接说明某具体工作者免征 FICA。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 个避免清单。",
        "Factors that may affect residency for tuition, taxes, licensing, benefits.": "可能影响学费、税务、执业资格、福利个居住身份因素。",
        "Failing to register on time may affect eligibility for federal benefits, federal jobs, and naturalization later, even though the requirement is federal. State DMV workflows can also trigger automatic registration, which applicants should understand before applying.": "未按时登记,可能影响将来个联邦福利、联邦工作㧯入籍资格,尽管系联邦要求。州 DMV 流程也可能触发自动登记。",
        "Family move": "全家搬屋",
        "Federal HealthCare.gov guidance describes a list of immigration statuses considered lawfully present for purposes of the Affordable Care Act marketplace, which includes many common nonimmigrant categories. These categories can purchase coverage without a five-year waiting period that applies in many Medicaid contexts.": "联邦 HealthCare.gov 指引描述咗一份对 ACA 市场视为「lawfully present」个移民身份清单,其中包括好多常见非移民类别;具体覆盖个类别清单可能变化,州市场可能采用㧯州相关个额外政策。",
        "Federal Medicaid and CHIP rules generally include a five-year waiting period for many qualified non-citizens after obtaining qualified status, with several federal exceptions. States may use an option that removes the waiting period for children and pregnant people, and some states cover certain groups with state funds.": "联邦 Medicaid 㧯 CHIP 规则一般为好多合资格非公民设定五年等待期(取得合资格身份后),并有若干联邦例外。各州可能采用 CHIPRA / ICHIA 选项,为合法居住个细仔抑系孕期人群豁免该等待期,某兜州还为唔符合联邦资格个群体提供州资金项目。",
        "Federal Medicare guidance generally describes eligibility for non-citizens who are lawfully admitted for permanent residence and have lived in the United States for five continuous years. Federal Medicaid rules for most nonimmigrants are narrower than for LPRs, with state-specific options for emergency Medicaid and for lawfully residing children and pregnant individuals.": "联邦 Medicare 指引一般描述,合法接收为永久居民并在美国连续居住五年个非公民个资格。联邦 Medicaid 规则对受联邦资助个合资格非公民通常设定五年等待期,各州可能为合法居住个细仔㧯孕期人士采用 CHIPRA 选项。",
        "Federal REAL ID rules require evidence of lawful status, and many states issue a REAL ID to nonimmigrant visa holders only with an expiration date that does not extend past the I-94, the visa, or another underlying federal document. Implementation differs between states, and standard (non-REAL-ID) options may or may not be offered.": "联邦 REAL ID 规则要求合法身份证明,好多州对非移民签证持有人签发个 REAL ID 个有效期唔会超过 I-94、签证抑系其他基础联邦文件个到期日,以反映联邦最低要求;具体处理因州而异。",
        "Federal SNAP, TANF, and similar programs apply a waiting period to many qualified non-citizens. Some states use state funds to operate replacement or supplemental programs that cover groups not eligible for the federal program, with differing rules.": "联邦 SNAP、TANF 㧯类似项目对好多合资格非公民设定等待期。某兜州用州资金运营替代抑系补充项目,以覆盖唔符合联邦项目资格个群体,各项目个分项各州唔同。",
        "Federal law": "联邦法律",
        "Federal law (INA section 265) generally directs non-citizens to report a change of address to USCIS within 10 days of moving, typically through Form AR-11 or the USCIS online change-of-address tool. The federal filing is separate from updating a state DMV record, an employer, a school, or the U.S. Postal Service.": "联邦法律(INA 第 265 条)一般要求非公民在搬屋后 10 日内向 USCIS 报告地址变更,通常通过 Form AR-11 抑系 USCIS 在线地址变更工具。该申报㧯 USPS 邮件转寄、州 DMV 地址㧯学校抑系雇主记录系分开个。",
        "Federal law generally requires motor vehicle offices to offer voter registration to applicants, and forms are screened for citizenship attestations. Non-citizens generally are not eligible to register for federal elections, and a registration record can later create immigration complications.": "联邦法律一般要求机动车机关向申请人提供选民登记,表格会查询公民身份声明。非公民一般无资格登记,但在 DMV 流程中可能仍会被询问。",
        "Federal residency for tax purposes determines whether worldwide income is reported, which IRS forms apply, and how an interstate move's first and last year are filed at the federal level, separately from state residency rules.": "出于税务目个个联邦居住身份决定全球收入系唔系申报、适用哪兜 IRS 表格,以及跨州搬屋首末年仰般在联邦层面申报(㧯各州各自个州税居住身份规则分开)。",
        "Federal rules govern which immigration statuses can purchase coverage and receive financial help through the Affordable Care Act marketplace, and those rules have changed. State-based marketplaces and state-funded programs add another layer that can differ between origin and destination.": "联邦规则规定哪些移民身份做得通过 Affordable Care Act 市场购买保险㧯获得财政帮助,该规则有变化。州个市场㧯州资金项目可能在联邦规则之外为某兜群体提供选项,各州个分项亦可能唔同。",
        "Federal tax authority": "联邦税务机关",
        "Federal tax authority general guidance": "联邦税务机关一般指引",
        "Filing Requirements, Residency, and Telecommuting FAQs": "申报要求、居住身份㧯远端办公常见问题",
        "Flags risk levels so you know where to focus": "标出风险等级,等你知爱重点关注么个所在",
        "Florida Board of Governors page on residency for tuition purposes for the State University System. flbog.edu returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Florida Board of Governors 关于 State University System 学费目个之居住身份个页面。flbog.edu 对非浏览器请求返回 403(Cloudflare),系已知误判。",
        "Florida FLHSMV documentation page for nonimmigrant applicants for driver licenses and identification cards.": "Florida FLHSMV 关于非移民申请驾照㧯身份卡个证件页面。",
        "Follow device language": "跟随设备语言",
        "For L-1, whether the new worksite is the same qualifying U.S. office described in the petition or a different one": "对 L-1 而言,新工作地点系唔系系申请中描述个同一合资格美国办公室,还系另一家",
        "For L-1A, L-1B, and O-1 status, USCIS treats a move to a new worksite as a material change in some fact patterns and not others, depending on what the original petition described and whether the new location is consistent with the approved terms. The analysis follows the underlying petition, not LCA-based MSA rules.": "对于 L-1A、L-1B 㧯 O-1 身份,USCIS 在某兜事实模式下将搬到新工作地点视为实质性变化,在另外一兜下唔系,取决于原始申请描述个内容,以及新地点系唔系仍属同一合资格雇主、办公室抑系演出/活动安排。",
        "For O-1, whether the new venue, event, engagement, or agent arrangement falls within the approved petition scope": "对 O-1 而言,新场馆、活动、演出抑系经纪人安排系唔系在已批准个申请范围内",
        "For federal tax purposes, a non-citizen is generally treated as a resident alien if they meet the Substantial Presence Test or hold lawful permanent resident status, with separate rules in IRS Publication 519 for exempt individuals (such as certain F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q students and scholars) whose days of presence may not count.": "出于联邦税务目个,非公民如符合 Substantial Presence Test 抑系持有合法永久居民身份,一般视为居民外国人;IRS Publication 519 㧯相关 IRS 页面中对到达年度㧯离境年度,以及 F、J、M、Q 类别个免计规则,设有专项条款。",
        "For nursing specifically, how the destination state treats primary state of residency under the Nurse Licensure Compact for a non-citizen who declares either the country of origin or the compact state, and any credentials-evaluation requirement (for example, CGFNS) for internationally educated applicants": "对护理而言,目的州对非公民申请人(声明原籍国抑系 Compact 州为主要居住州)在 Nurse Licensure Compact 下个主要居住州仰般处理",
        "Form AR-11 paper version posted on uscis.gov.": "uscis.gov 上发布个 Form AR-11 纸质版。",
        "Frame AR-11 as a federal reporting step to verify, not a guarantee of status. Do not state that any specific status category is or is not covered without source. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing such as the i-word, the p-words, and penalty-avoidance phrasing). Direct readers to consult a licensed immigration attorney for status-specific guidance.": "请将 AR-11 表述为爱核实个联邦报告步骤,唔系身份保证。无来源个情形下,唔好说任何具体身份类别系唔系适用。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 个避免清单(法律结论性表述㧯规避处罚个措辞)。",
        "Frame as a federal requirement that may apply, with a nonimmigrant exception that may apply based on continuous valid status. Do not state that any specific person is or is not required to register. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "请表述为可能适用个联邦要求,根据连续有效身份可能适用个非移民例外。唔好直接说明任何具体人系唔系需要登记。请用中性表述。",
        "Frame as items to verify in IRS Publication 519 and with a qualified tax preparer. Do not state a person is a dual-status filer for a particular year. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "请表述为爱在 IRS Publication 519 㧯合资格税务专业人士处核实个项目。唔好直接说明某人某年度系双重身份申报人。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 个避免清单。",
        "Frame as items to verify with CMS and the destination-state Medicaid agency. Federal rules have changed and may continue to change. Do not state a person is or is not eligible. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "请表述为爱向 CMS 㧯目的州 Medicaid 机构核实个项目。联邦规则有变化,可能继续变化。唔好直接说明某人系唔系符合资格。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 个避免清单。",
        "Frame as items to verify with IRS Publication 519 and a tax preparer. Do not state a person is or is not a resident alien for federal tax purposes. Use may apply and rules differ by jurisdiction. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "请表述为爱向 IRS Publication 519 㧯税务专业人士核实个项目。唔好直接说明某人在联邦税务目个上系唔系居民外国人。请用「可能适用」㧯「各司法管辖区个规则唔同」。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 个避免清单。",
        "Frame as items to verify with the DSO or J-1 sponsor and Study in the States or ICE guidance. This item is specific to F-1, M-1, and J-1 status. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "请将其表述为爱向 DSO 抑系 J-1 赞助方核实个项目,并参考 Study in the States 抑系 ICE 指引。该项目专门针对 F-1、M-1 㧯 J-1 身份。请避免 iOS SafeCopy 个避免清单(法律结论性表述㧯规避处罚个措辞)。",
        "Frame as items to verify with the current HealthCare.gov or state-based marketplace lists. Do not state any specific category is or is not on the lawfully present list, since federal rules have changed. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "请表述为爱向 HealthCare.gov 抑系州市场当前清单核实个项目。唔好直接说明任何具体类别系唔系在「lawfully present」清单上,因为联邦规则有变化。请遵循 SafeCopy 避免清单。",
        "Full disclaimer:": "完整免责声明:",
        "General information only. Not legal advice. Verify with official sources.": "净系一般资讯。唔系法律建议。请向官方来源核实。",
