        "MoveSafe provides general legal and administrative information based on publicly available sources. It does not provide legal advice, does not create an attorney-client relationship, and should not be used as a substitute for advice from a licensed attorney in your jurisdiction. Laws and agency rules change frequently. Always verify information with official sources before making decisions.": "MoveSafe 基于公开来源提供一般法律㧯行政资讯。佢唔提供法律建议,唔建立律师客户关系,唔做得用来替代你所在司法管辖区持证律师个建议。法律㧯机构规则常常变。做决定之前请永远向官方来源核实资讯。",
