        "USCIS archive page summarizing the 2015 Simeio Solutions final guidance and the LCA-amendment trigger for worksite changes outside the MSA.": "USCIS 存档页,概述 2015 年 Simeio Solutions 最终指引以及超出 MSA 个工作地点变更触发 LCA 修改个要求。",
