        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that an H-1B worker moving to a new worksite within the same MSA or area of intended employment as the existing LCA does not require a new LCA or an amended H-1B petition, although the existing LCA may still need to be posted at the new worksite. The federal AR-11 address change requirement still applies to the worker.": "USCIS 指引一般表明,H-1B 工作者搬到㧯当前 LCA 同一 MSA 抑系拟定就业区域内个新工作地点,唔需要新 LCA 抑系修改个 H-1B 申请,但需要在新工作地点张贴现有 LCA,并通过 AR-11 进行地址更新。",
