        "Under 22 CFR Part 62, J-1 program sponsors maintain the SEVIS record and monitor the site of activity for each exchange visitor. A move that changes residence, site of activity, or host organization generally triggers an exchange-visitor reporting obligation to the sponsor and a sponsor update to SEVIS.": "根据 22 CFR Part 62,J-1 项目赞助方维护 SEVIS 记录,并监督每位交流访问者个活动地点。涉及住所、活动地点抑系接待机构变更个搬屋,一般触发 10 日内向赞助方个报告;某兜变更可能需要赞助方个事前授权抑系国务院批准。",
        "Under USCIS guidance following Matter of Simeio Solutions (2015), an H-1B worker's move to a worksite outside the metropolitan statistical area (MSA) or area of intended employment listed on the current Labor Condition Application (LCA) is generally a material change that calls for a new LCA and an amended H-1B petition.": "根据 Matter of Simeio Solutions(2015)之后个 USCIS 指引,H-1B 工作者搬到当前 LCA 上列出个都市统计区(MSA)抑系拟定就业区域之外个工作地点,一般触发新 LCA 㧯修改后个 Form I-129,而唔系净系工作地点公告。",
